§oThis quest technically requires all the previous quests it depends on, not just one. I figured it would be nice if you could see all the requirements ahead of time.§r

Here, I'm also throwing a §aLV Machine Hull§r in this quest. That's what you need to make any §7LV§r machine! I am feeling so generous, that this quest will grant you a second hull, free of charge!

§6Once you complete this Quest and the LV Motor Quest, you are ready to move on to the LV Age.§r
